metadata.name: OUT OF MY MIND
metadata.description:
With all the comments and taunts you feed in me,  
 filling me up loosing  myself, 
doubting who I am ,  
 questioning myself, my pride, my love , my whole existence,  
No place left to think, your words captured the place I think,  
I am worthless , your words not mine, yet i hear them day and night,  
I hope you are happy now that you are where you wanted to be ,  
I am out of my mind where your words are filled ,  
I am out of my mind , numbing the pain.
